<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>CRAFTSTORY</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{box-sizing:border-box}
body{margin:0;font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;background:#0f0f10;color:#fff}
header{padding:30px;text-align:center;background:#111;border-bottom:1px solid #222}
header h1{margin:0;font-size:32px;letter-spacing:2px}
header p{opacity:.7}
nav{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:30px;padding:15px;background:#151515;flex-wrap:wrap}
nav a{color:white;text-decoration:none;font-weight:500}
nav a:hover{color:#00e0ff}
.hero{padding:90px 20px;text-align:center;background:linear-gradient(145deg,#121212,#1c1c1c)}
.hero h2{font-size:42px;margin-bottom:10px}
.hero p{opacity:.8}
.products{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:30px;padding:60px 40px}
.card{background:#181818;border-radius:16px;padding:20px;text-align:center;transition:.3s;border:1px solid #242424}
.card:hover{transform:translateY(-8px);border-color:#00e0ff}
.card img{width:100%;border-radius:10px}
.card h3{margin:15px 0 5px}
button{background:#00e0ff;border:none;padding:12px 18px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer}
button:hover{background:#00bcd4}
.section{padding:70px 20px;text-align:center}
.gallery{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:20px;padding:40px}
.gallery img{width:100%;border-radius:12px}
.review{background:#181818;border:1px solid #242424;margin:15px auto;padding:18px;border-radius:10px;max-width:500px}
.contact{background:#111}
footer{text-align:center;padding:30px;background:#0a0a0a;border-top:1px solid #222}
.tiktok-btn{position:fixed;bottom:25px;right:25px;background:#00e0ff;color:#000;padding:14px 18px;border-radius:50px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;box-shadow:0 0 15px rgba(0,224,255,0.6)}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
<h1>CRAFTSTORY</h1>
<p>Creative 3D Printed Creations</p>
</header>

<nav>
<a href="#home">Home</a>
<a href="#shop">Products</a>
<a href="#gallery">Gallery</a>
<a href="#about">About</a>
<a href="#contact">Contact</a>
</nav>

<section id="home" class="hero">
<h2>Premium 3D Printed Designs</h2>
<p>Custom creations, desk toys, decor, and unique prints made with precision.</p>
<p>Message us directly to order your design.</p>
</section>

<section id="shop" class="products">

<div class="card">
<img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400" alt="product">
<h3>Articulated Dragon</h3>
<p>Flexible 3D Printed Dragon</p>
<button onclick="order('Articulated Dragon')">Order via TikTok</button>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400" alt="product">
<h3>Desk Organizer</h3>
<p>Modern Minimalist Desk Tool</p>
<button onclick="order('Desk Organizer')">Order via TikTok</button>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400" alt="product">
<h3>Custom Print</h3>
<p>Your design, professionally printed</p>
<button onclick="order('Custom Print')">Order via TikTok</button>
</div>

</section>

<section id="gallery" class="gallery">
<img src="https://via.placeholder.com/500">
<img src="https://via.placeholder.com/500">
<img src="https://via.placeholder.com/500">
<img src="https://via.placeholder.com/500">
</section>

<section id="about" class="section">
<h2>About CRAFTSTORY</h2>
<p>CRAFTSTORY specializes in high quality 3D printed creations including articulated models, desk accessories, toys, and custom prints. Every piece is carefully printed using precision machines and quality materials.</p>
</section>

<section class="section">
<h2>Customer Reviews</h2>
<div class="review">⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ "Amazing quality and smooth prints!"</div>
<div class="review">⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ "Very creative designs. Highly recommended."</div>
</section>

<section id="contact" class="section contact">
<h2>Contact Us</h2>
<p>Send us a message on TikTok to place an order.</p>
<p>Email: your@email.com</p>
<p>TikTok: @craftstory</p>
<p>Location: Philippines</p>
</section>

<footer>
<p>© 2026 CRAFTSTORY</p>
</footer>

<a class="tiktok-btn" href="https://tiktok.com" target="_blank">Order on TikTok</a>

<script>
function order(product){
alert('You selected: '+product+'\nPlease message CRAFTSTORY on TikTok to order.');
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
